==Russian==
===Etymology===
From Old Church Slavonic [[бъіти]].

===Verb===
'''быть''' (byt’) ''[[impf.]]'', '''[[бывать]]''' (byvát’) ''[[iterative aspect]]''
# to [[be]]

===Usage notes===
Omitted in the present tense except in the third-person singular, which is used occasionally to express possession or definition.

===Conjugation===
*'''быть''' (''[[imperfective aspect]]'')


